  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To observe the influence of different methods titrating PEEP on right heart function and
      pulmonary artery pressure in ARDS patients .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      30 patients who diagnosed as ARDS were included in this study.Then set PEEP with respectively
      ARDS net 、EIT and Esophageal Pressure in Breathing Machine . Recorded diameter of right and
      left ventricular TAM TAPSE pulmonary artery pressure.Objective to evaluate the correlation
      between the level of PEEP in three methods and the right heart function and pulmonary artery
      pressure in ARDS patients .
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
